Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:25.92,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\c&HF9F153&\pos(538,353)}我妻由乃篇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好玩的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊 為什麼要來追我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個玩偶裝是怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有閒工夫和他耗著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不阻止天野同學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹啥啊 沒看我現在正忙嗎
